                </h3>
                <h4 class="text-dark dark:text-light">
                  User-centered design thinking meets technical implementation.
                  Great software should be both powerful and beautiful.
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
